Hello everybody, my team is using TalonFX/Falcon 500’s on our robot this year, unfortunately we had ran out of them, but we had a spare NEO motor.

The NEO Motor is connected to a Spark MAX, and the NEO has an integrated sensor, although I’m unsure how to get the velocity, or position from the motor using REV’s Java API.

(i.e in CTRE’s API it would be “motor.getSelectedSensorPosition();”)

Any help is greatly appreciated :>
